            <title>[CASSANDRA-19846] Allow looking up local tables in nodetool getendpoints</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-19846</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
